**About**
----

**Verelox B.V.** is an unmanaged hosting provider based in The Hague, The Netherlands. 

Providing VPS and dedicated servers since 2014, we guarantee that any issues you encounter will be resolved in a professional way and a timely fashion.

**Features**
----

1. Intel Xeon E3 and E5 3.2+ GHz processors with up to RAID 10 arrays.
2. 1Gbps network speed with IPv6 support.
3. KVM Virtualization + noVNC/Console access.
4. Custom ISO directly from the control panel: upload from your own URL or use one of our predefined ISOs.
5. Hourly billing + API.
6. DDoS protection included with all plans.
7. Free/unmetered incoming bandwidth - fair use.
8. Rescue mode, startup scripts, configurable downtime notifications/monitors, downgrade/upgrade any time.

[[View all]](https://verelox.com/cloud/features)

